longBusinessSummary: Tourn International AB (publ) develops technology for influencer marketing and social media. It serves brands and influencers. The company was formerly known as INEV Studios AB (publ) and changed its name to Tourn International AB (publ) in 2015. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
